	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">For me, this issue boils down to two things:<br />
<br />
1) What is your word worth?  You click "I ACCEPT" each and every time you play to a EULA that forbids plat buying and selling.  So.  You said you wouldn't do it.  If you sell or buy plat, what is your word worth now?  Well?  Let me tell you what it's worth.  Zip.<br />
<br />
2) Plat buying supports plat farming.  Don't come whining to me about high-cash areas and highly-desirable items being perma-camped if a) you also go around saying plat buying doesn't affect you, or b) you've bought plat.<br />
<br />
The first point is the most important to me.  My word is worth more to me than pixels on a screen.  Is yours?</font></p>
	
